Q1. Which statement best describes the business problem that Accenture is tasked to address for this project?

i) The clients financial stability has rapidly declined due to COVID-19 and they need to find new market opportunities to increase revenue.
ii) The client is looking to raise a significant amount of money through private investment and needs support with this.
iii) The client has reached a massive scale within recent years and does not have the resources internally to handle it.
iv) The client has reached a massive scale within recent years and is having big issues retaining and hiring the best talent. The client needs help to find out why this problem has arisen.

CORRECT ANSWER :- iii) The client has reached a massive scale within recent years and does not have the resources internally to handle it.





Q2 Which statement lists the three requirements that Accenture is tasked to fulfill for this project?

i) Audit of financial history, IPO recommendations, analysis of popular content .
ii) Big data analytics, recommendations for recruitment, analysis of popular content .
iii) Audit of big data practice, recommendations for IPO, analysis of market opportunities .
iv) Audit of big data practice, recommendations for IPO, analysis of popular content .

CORRECT ANSWER :- iv) Audit of big data practice, recommendations for IPO, analysis of popular content.          
